<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@100;300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />

    <title>Rexify API | Documentation</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    //- <svg class="illustration" height="80vh" width="70vw">
    //-   <use href="img/developer-team.svg#icon-developer"></use>
    //- </svg>
    <header class="header">
      <div class="announcement">
        <div class="announcement__heading">
          //- <svg width="4rem" height="4rem">
          //-   <use href="img/megaphone.svg#icon-announcement"></use>
          //- </svg>
          <h2 class="heading-secondary">More products will be added soonðŸ”¥</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="container">
      <div class="flex u-margin-bottom-medium">
        <h1 class="heading-primary">Rexify API v1 Documentation</h1>
        <div class="div flex">
          <svg height="3rem" width="3rem" class="color-filter--red">
            <use href="img/linkedin.svg#icon-linkedin"></use>
          </svg>
          <p class="insta-id"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/akash-shah-60b2781b9">@_aakash__shah</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="paragraph u-margin-bottom-small">This API provides products for building an Ecommerce App.</p>
      <div class="important u-margin-bottom-medium">
        <h3 class="heading-tertiary u-margin-bottom-very-small">Important details</h3>
        <ul class="important__list u-margin-bottom-small">
          <li>No need to use CORS proxy or API key</li>
          <li>Search terms are limited. Search for "t-shirts" or another product from this list &rarr;
            <a class="search-list" href="#query-list">Search Queries</a>
          </li>
          <li>Supports up to 100 API requests per hour</li>
          <li>Only GET requests allowed</li>
        </ul>
        //- <button class="btn">Generate your API Key</button>
      </div>
      <div class="get-request u-margin-bottom-small">
        <h2 class="heading-secondary u-margin-bottom-small">Get all products</h2>
        <p class="paragraph">Allowed Methods : <span class="http-method-lable">GET</span></p>
        <p class="paragraph">GET : Returns a list of products for a specific search query</p>
        <p class="paragraph">Path: <code>https://rexify-api.herokuapp.com/api/v1/products</code></p>
      </div>
      <h3 class="heading-tertiary u-margin-bottom-small">Parameters</h3>
      <table class="table u-margin-bottom-medium">
        <tr>
          <th>Parameter</th>
          <th>Required</th>
          <th>Description</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Search</td>
          <td>Yes</td>
          <td>Search text. For example <code>search=jeans</code></td>
        </tr>
        //- <tr>
        //-   <td>key</td>
        //-   <td>Yes (for <span class="http-method-lable">POST</span>)</td>
        //-   <td>The Rexify API key</td>
        //- </tr>
      </table>
      <p class="paragraph u-margin-bottom-medium">Example: <code>https://rexify-api.herokuapp.com/api/v1/products?search=jeans</code></p>

      //- GET : with Id : 63c2b30832a56cbf99c2834e
      <div class="get-request u-margin-bottom-small">
        <h2 class="heading-secondary u-margin-bottom-small">Get products with ID</h2>
        <p class="paragraph">Allowed Methods : <span class="http-method-lable">GET</span></p>
        <p class="paragraph">GET : Returns the details about a specific product</p>
        <p class="paragraph">Path: <code>https://rexify-api.herokuapp.com/api/v1/products/:id</code></p>
      </div>
      <h3 class="heading-tertiary u-margin-bottom-small">Parameters</h3>
      <table class="table u-margin-bottom-medium">
        <tr>
          <th>Parameter</th>
          <th>Required</th>
          <th>Description</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>id</td>
          <td>Yes</td>
          <td>Product id. For example <code>id : 63c2b30832a56cbf99c2834e</code></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p class="paragraph u-margin-bottom-medium">Example: <code>https://rexify-api.herokuapp.com/api/v1/products/63c2b30832a56cbf99c2834e</code></p>


      //- Available list of search terms
      <div id="query-list" class="queries">
        <h2 class="heading-secondary u-margin-bottom-small">Available Search Queries</h2>
        <ul class="important__list">
          <li>jeans</li>
          <li>t-shirts</li>
          <li>shirts</li>
          <li>shoes</li>
          <li>plazzos</li>
          <li>A-line dress</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
